元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/111%2c%e8%8b%97%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c332%2c20220527%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,111,苗交簡,332,20220527,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"苗交簡","JNO":"332","JDATE":"20220527","JTITLE":"公共危險"}